    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚因通胀担忧延长利率暂停期限第三个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/serbia-extends-rate-pause-for-third-month-on-inflation-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞尔维亚央行连续第三个月维持借贷成本不变，在持续的价格压力和通胀放缓速度的不确定性下，延长了货币宽松的暂停期限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/serbia-extends-rate-pause-for-third-month-on-inflation-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 11:03:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券市场中性利率猜谜游戏风险高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/neutral-rate-guessing-game-comes-with-high-stakes-in-bond-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在华尔街的债券交易柜台，似乎每个人对中性利率都有自己的看法。中性利率是 3.3%。不，是 4.5%。实际上，是 2.4%。而且，一周五天，整天都在变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/neutral-rate-guessing-game-comes-with-high-stakes-in-bond-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
